definitions.definition: ( chiefly in the plural ) A person from Myanmar or of Burmese descent.
( zoology ) A medium-sized, short-haired domestic cat of a breed originating in Thailand .

main_definition: ( chiefly in the plural ) A person from Myanmar or of Burmese descent.
secondary_definitions: ( zoology ) A medium-sized, short-haired domestic cat of a breed originating in Thailand .

definitions.definition: The Sino-Tibetan official language of the country Burma. Also known as Myanmar (which is the name preferred by the country's current government).
The script in which the Burmese language is written.
